.000Z","msg":"又嬴, 合成基因野, 支那或能量產加美尤"},{"pid":"7493c72f666296c935269ebe5918268e9ae1d504","tid":2188150,"uid":52358,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T05:25:54.000Z","msg":"呢次真係食鹽多過食米<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b6c6a0fe550282043d3b665222e11a89ff5162e","tid":2188150,"uid":363413,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T05:28:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d4996c15d17ac82eeb5f75187da010dffa9093c","tid":2188150,"uid":187232,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T05:29:18.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">沿海濕地生態玩撚完<br />\n中國濕地生物嘅末日</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n南豐村村民龍先清說，村里有幾千畝灘塗地，以前種出來的香蕉和甘蔗，還沒大拇指粗，沒想到現在灘塗地也能長出糧食，很了不起。<br />\n陳日勝團隊今年早造不僅擴大了「海水稻」的種植面積，還在稻田裡養殖魚蝦蟹，提升經濟效益。<br />\n中國工程院院士、雜交水稻之父袁隆平估算，中國約有15億畝荒蕪鹽鹼地，利用好1億畝種植「海水稻」，即便畝產只有300公斤，也能產出300億公斤糧食，解決8000萬人的糧食問題。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原文網址: 廣東「海水稻」展開收割　總產量估1600噸「10月首次上市銷售」 | ETtoday大陸新聞 | ETtoday新聞雲 <a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20200904/1801132.htm#ixzz6X33DT5n3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20200904%2F1801132.htm%23ixzz6X33DT5n3&d=HMiOmB7b1AqxO%2BCwCPl1cYVo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=644b93ff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20200904/1801132.htm#ixzz6X33DT5n3</a> <br />\nFollow us: @ETtodaynet on Twitter | ETtoday on Facebook"},{"pid":"83fa0332f3588d2a3f373e57bfb50035b1049776","tid":2188150,"uid":26770,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T05:30:13.000Z","msg":"海水稻成本係普通水稻五倍....."},{"pid":"c2ee1ef59593c47ade1c25b3aae3bdc0415a17bc","tid":2188150,"uid":14103,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"quote":{